Chrysler Corp's Chrysler Motors Corpsaid its Chrysler Training Corp non-profit organization soldthe name and assets of its Motech Auto Mechanic and Body ShopSchools to O/E Corp of Troy, Mich.    The sale price was not disclosed.    Under the Internal Revenue Service code, proceeds from thesale of Motech must be donated to another tax-exempt nonprofitorganization. Chrysler did not reveal the name of the groupthat received the proceeds. Reuter&#3;